    "In order to meet the FCS's demand for electricity while reducing the cost of production and energy loss, energy management and optimization are consequently crucial for the mixed energy system 33.",
    "A mixed-integer linear programming-based energy management technique was created as part of a model reference adaptive control to address this issue and enhance the charging station's performance.",
